filterByNAICS

  • filterByNAICS(naicsCodes: string | string[], sectors: Sector[]): Sector[]

  • Maps the given NAICS codes to BEA codes and then filters the given sectors to only include sectors with a matching BEA code.

    Parameters

    • naicsCodes: string | string[]
    • sectors: Sector[]

    Returns Sector[]

toBEA

  • toBEA(naicsCodes: string | string[]): string[]

  • Returns a set of correspondig BEA codes for the given NAICS codes. Note that a NAICS code can be mapped to multiple BEA codes so that the returned list can contain more codes than the input list

    Parameters

    • naicsCodes: string | string[]

    Returns string[]
